### ==========================================
### 标讯模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token（管理员）
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

### 保存 Token
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：获取标讯列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders?page=0&size=10&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：多条件筛选
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders?status=TRACKING&sourceType=MANUAL&page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 正常流程：创建标讯
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "API测试标讯-{{$randomInt 1 9999}}",
  "source": "API测试",
  "budget": 1000000,
  "deadline": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "status": "TRACKING"
}

### 4. 边界：创建标讯缺少必填字段
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 5. 边界：预算为负数
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "预算异常标讯",
  "source": "API测试",
  "budget": -100
}

### 6. 边界：标讯标题过长
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "A",
  "source": "API测试"
}

### 7. 边界：分页参数异常（超大 pageSize）
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders?page=0&size=99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 边界：分页越界
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders?page=99999&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 正常流程：标讯详情
@tenderId = 1
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/{{tenderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. 边界：不存在的标讯
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. 正常流程：标讯评估
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/{{tenderId}}/evaluation/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "evaluationResult": "PASS",
  "remark": "API测试评估通过"
}

### 12. 边界：非 owner 操作（需要 sales 角色 token）
# 先用 staff 角色登录
# @name staffLogin
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "xiaowang",
  "password": "123456"
}

@staffToken = {{staffLogin.response.body.data.token}}

### 13. 越权访问：staff 创建标讯（应允许，但检查权限边界）
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Staff创建的标讯-{{$randomInt 1 9999}}",
  "source": "手动录入",
  "budget": 50000
}

### 14. 正常流程：转派标讯
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/{{tenderId}}/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assigneeId": 2,
  "remark": "转派测试"
}

### 15. 正常流程：市场洞察
GET http://localhost:18081/api/market-insight/insight
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. 正常流程：AI 评分
POST http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/{{tenderId}}/match-score/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. 正常流程：导出标讯
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/export?page=0&size=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
